Requires Selenium for Python.

Install it like this (Ubuntu/Debian):
sudo apt-get install python-pip
sudo pip install -U selenium

Or for Mac
Install pip, instruction at http://www.pip-installer.org/en/latest/installing.html
sudo pip install -U selenium

Get updated wine.json from http://barnivore.com/api

Run python getwineproducers.py | tee results
and get the matching wines from 'results' afterwards
